https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=21869	10080
Linus Torvalds<a href="http://lwn.net/Articles/421638/">发布了2.6.37 kernel</a>。新版的<a href="http://kernelnewbies.org/Linux_2_6_37">主要特性</a>包括：<i>
